description: This Chainlink VRF common Plezier purrs with a rating of 47, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 94, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, Leverage for East, 5 for South, and 5 for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/70472-76554-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [94 Votes, Common]
